%%{init: {"theme": "base"}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Candidato
    participant A as Agente IA
    participant S as scan.mjs
    participant P as providers/
    participant W as Playwright
    participant WS as WebSearch
    participant PL as pipeline.md
    participant H as scan-history.tsv

    U->>A: /career-ops scan
    A->>A: Lê portals.yml + histórico + dedup sources

    Note over A,S: Nível 0 — preferir zero-token
    A->>S: node src/scan/scan.mjs
    S->>P: fetch por empresa (concorrência 10)
    P-->>S: jobs[]
    S->>S: title_filter + location_filter + dedup
    S->>PL: append Pending (se não --dry-run)
    S->>H: registra added / skipped
    S-->>A: local_parser_ok + resumo

    loop Empresas sem local_parser_ok
        Note over A,W: Nível 1 — Playwright
        A->>W: careers_url batches 3–5
        W-->>A: listings
    end

    loop Empresas com api: sem parser ok
        Note over A: Nível 2 — API ATS
        A->>A: WebFetch + parse provider
    end

    loop search_queries enabled
        Note over A,WS: Nível 3 — descoberta ampla
        A->>WS: query site:
        WS-->>A: resultados
        A->>A: filtra local_parser_ok
        loop cada URL nova Nível 3
            A->>W: liveness check (sequencial)
            W-->>A: active / expired
        end
    end

    A->>A: Merge + filtros finais
    A->>PL: novas linhas Pending
    A->>H: skipped_title / skipped_dup / skipped_expired
    A-->>U: Resumo + "→ /career-ops pipeline"
